# @baseUrl = http://localhost:5258
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8090

### 1) Получить список доступных языков
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/languages
Accept: application/json

### 2) Успешный прогон (ожидаем OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/code-execution/test-run
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "code": "print(input())",
  "language": "python",
  "testCases": [
    {
      "order": 1,
      "input": "hello",
      "expectedOutput": "hello"
    },
    {
      "order": 2,
      "input": "world",
      "expectedOutput": "world"
    }
  ],
  "maxTimeSeconds": 3,
  "maxMemoryMb": 128
}

### 3) Неверный ответ (ожидаем WA)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/code-execution/test-run
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "code": "print('wrong')",
  "language": "python",
  "testCases": [
    {
      "order": 1,
      "input": "hello",
      "expectedOutput": "hello"
    }
  ],
  "maxTimeSeconds": 3,
  "maxMemoryMb": 128
}

### 4) Ошибка выполнения (ожидаем RE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/code-execution/test-run
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "code": "x = 1 / 0\nprint(x)",
  "language": "python",
  "testCases": [
    {
      "order": 1,
      "input": "",
      "expectedOutput": ""
    }
  ],
  "maxTimeSeconds": 3,
  "maxMemoryMb": 128
}

### 5) Неподдерживаемый язык (ожидаем none / ошибка конфигурации)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/code-execution/test-run
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "code": "print('hello')",
  "language": "python2",
  "testCases": [
    {
      "order": 1,
      "input": "",
      "expectedOutput": "hello"
    }
  ],
  "maxTimeSeconds": 3,
  "maxMemoryMb": 128
}

### 6) Пустой список тестов (ожидаем 400 EMPTY_TEST_CASES)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/code-execution/test-run
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "code": "print('hello')",
  "language": "python",
  "testCases": []
}
